com.emarsys.predict

Interface Storage


  • public interface Storage
    Interface for accessing and modifying save and retrieve persistent key-value pairs.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      java.lang.Object get(java.lang.String key)
      Returns the value to which the specified key is stored, or null if the store not contains value for the key.
      void put(java.lang.String key, java.lang.Object value)
      Set a value in the storage for the key.

    • Method Detail

      • put

        void put(java.lang.String key,
         java.lang.Object value)
        Set a value in the storage for the key. If the storage previously contained a mapping for the key, the old value is replaced by the specified value.
        Parameters:
        key - the key with which the specified value is to be stored
        value - value to be stored with the specified key

      • get

        java.lang.Object get(java.lang.String key)
        Returns the value to which the specified key is stored, or null if the store not contains value for the key.
        Parameters:
        key - the key whose stored value is to be returned
        Returns:
        the value to which the specified key is stored, or null
